c=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生先係最唔會走既行業，醫生讀咁多書仲要專科一去外國度度都有保護主義考唔番個牌點算？<br />\n係香港高薪做皇帝日日睇樓食好西唔好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同當年醫護罷工一樣吹大左，見堆medic人無一個識既有join，個個專科training得鬼閒陪你癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過講事實就會比班無腦弱智仔屈係5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T18:55:51.000Z","msg":"同感<br />\n香港專科搵到的錢其他國家搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n但唔少人係打算送屋企人走自己係香港搵到最後一秒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:12:11.000Z","msg":"無錯，這刻係留下，但仔女就想佢去外國。不過計返條數，香港人工係高，但樓價同樣高。外國人工低，同樣樓價亦低，餘下的是心理關口。<br />\n<br />\n香港醫生訓練不下於歐美，去生活相信無問題。"},{"pid":"967f12784e2dc10fddf688d4c05dba7c900f1efe","tid":2479331,"uid":124585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:14:02.000Z","msg":"樓價GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f43868b0282e2b6da6eca6a3dfa2f35819718a4","tid":2479331,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:14:28.000Z","msg":"多撚謝支共港共"},{"pid":"fb52cfc9af565e260d24d835c4b9f91390a13fb6","tid":2479331,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T23:15:08.000Z","msg":"反送中事件，大家爭取過勇武過，呢個腐敗政權無得救，移民其實係保命。"}]}